{"about_the_game":"<strong>Don't leave the town, don't make a mistake.</strong><br><br><strong>Motherland</strong> (A sad fairytale for adults) is an indie-game that allows you to immerse in the atmosphere of a provincial town during the epidemic.<br>You are a tourist who came to Russia from another country. By the will of fate you find yourself in a provincial town. Now you can finally get to know the local traditions and culture. But when the time to return home came, the borders got closed...<br>Now you have to stay in a small rented apartment. Staying in a damp, poorly heated place for too long makes you ill. You decide to go outside to get some fresh air and buy medicine at the local pharmacy.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immersive gameplay<br></li><li>The atmosphere of a small provincial town<br></li><li>Non-linear narrative<br></li><li>Variety of fully-voiced colorful characters<br></li><li>Freedom of action (within the limits of the law)<br></li><li>Vast open world<br></li><li>Undying and iconic Russian panel houses<br></li><li>Omnipresent sense of sadness<br></li><li>Everlasting sorrow<br></li><li>Nonsense and jokes</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">(Maddyson is trying to leave Zamkadsk)</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791030/extras/1111.jpg?t=1707917629\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Zamkadsk","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1791030/d63e120e642a2e80f636610faae1d88851e38eaa.jpg"},{"name":"Exodus","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1791030/4870789586e96b47e6d759f8db786464f24ce456.jpg"},{"name":"Light up this world","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1791030/81799a3fbff4260b452f0707de617cc6b54284e9.jpg"},{"name":"Insure your life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1791030/d417ef77fe739